        <p>Twelve years later we run a 4,500 sq. ft. flagship store, an online catalogue of 1,200+ products, and a service workshop that handles over 800 repairs a month. We never stopped being that shop that takes thirty minutes to explain why a product is right — or wrong — for you.</p>

