  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section id="faq" class="section faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Got Questions?</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Quick answers to the things customers ask us most. Can't find yours? <a href="#footer-contact" style="color:var(--accent)">Contact us directly.</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            Do you offer EMI on purchases?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Yes — we partner with four major banks (Electra Finance, Zenith Credit, Nova Bank, and PayEasy) to offer no-cost EMI on purchases above ₹5,000, with tenures from 3 to 24 months. EMI is available both in-store and online.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            What is your return and exchange policy?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>We offer a 10-day no-questions return window on all products, provided the item is in its original packaging with all accessories. Defective items are replaced or refunded within 24 hours of reporting. Some sealed software and personalised items are non-returnable.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            How long does a typical repair take?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Screen replacements and battery swaps are usually done in 2–4 hours. More complex repairs like motherboard work or data recovery can take 1–3 business days. You'll receive an SMS update at every stage, and our workshop tracking portal lets you check status in real time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            Is there a warranty on repaired devices?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>All repairs carry a 90-day service warranty. If the same fault recurs within that period, we fix it free of charge. We use only OEM-grade or genuine spare parts, and every repair comes with a detailed service invoice.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            Do you ship products outside Hyderabad?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Yes — we ship across India via Electra Express Logistics. Delivery typically takes 2–5 business days depending on your pin code. Orders above ₹2,999 qualify for free standard shipping. Expedited overnight delivery is available for an additional charge.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            Can I trade in a device that's damaged?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Absolutely. We accept devices in any condition — working, cracked, water-damaged, or non-functional. Damaged devices receive a lower trade-in value, which our team calculates transparently on the spot. You're under no obligation to proceed if the offer doesn't suit you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            Do you carry products from all major brands?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>We stock products from over 40 brands across our categories — including Voltex, NovaTech, Lumina, AetherSound, ZenCore, and more. If you're looking for a specific model we don't currently carry, we can typically source it within 3–5 business days through our distributor network.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item" data-open="false">
          <button class="faq-q">
            Are your refurbished products reliable?
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>All certified pre-owned devices go through a 47-point inspection covering hardware, battery health, software, and cosmetic condition. They're graded A (like new), B (minor wear), or C (visible wear) — clearly labelled so you know exactly what you're buying. Each carries a 6-month warranty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
